title: Can't seem to interact in any other way with the site
body: I'm unable to upvote anything or comment elsewhere. help?

replies.body: Your profile might have been out of sync.  Make sure to use the[ syncing tool ](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support/fos1aFEB-boards-profile-syncing-tool)if this is still an issue!

You needed to update your in game level with the forum, and it was updated when you posted here. Another way to update your level is by using the [syncing tool](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support/fos1aFEB-boards-profile-syncing-tool). You should be able to do everything now!
